# This folder is the integration bridge between the Data Pipeline and the Chatbot.
#
# DATA FLOW:
#   [Airflow Pipeline]
#       crawl → clean → load Neo4j → export_csv_to_shared (writes here)
#                                            ↓
#   [shared_data/]  ←── pipeline writes CSV files here after every run
#         ↓
#   [Neo4j container]  ← mounts this folder as /var/lib/neo4j/import
#         ↓
#   [Chatbot]  ← reads from Neo4j via Bolt (no need to re-ingest CSV manually)
#
# Files produced by the pipeline:
#   nodes_group.csv, nodes_topic.csv, nodes_problem.csv, nodes_answer.csv
#   nodes_problem_supplement.csv, nodes_answer_supplement.csv
#   rels_has_topic.csv, rels_has_problem.csv, rels_has_answer.csv
#   rels_has_answer_supplement.csv
